  "detailed_description": "<h1>MEANDERS - NEW LEVELS AVAILABLE!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Overchunked</strong> is a game about a giant circular saw constantly moving forward: steer it left and right to guide its course, dodge obstacles, <i>TNT</i> explosives and destroy the rest of the environment to obtain points!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/833910/extras/bad6843affe1019d952bc1889434f713.poster.avif?t=1569935230\" width=600 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/833910/extras/bad6843affe1019d952bc1889434f713.webm?t=1569935230\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/833910/extras/bad6843affe1019d952bc1889434f713.mp4?t=1569935230\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/833910/extras/8d31ca7568086eac5e168add4bf8a68e.webp?t=1569935230\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>FAST GAMEPLAY:</i></strong> easy to play hard to master<br></li><li><strong><i>DESTRUCTION IS SATISFACTION:</i></strong> destroy everything on your path and avoid obstacles<br></li><li><strong><i>EVERCHANGING WORLD:</i></strong> enjoy the dynamic procedurally generated map<br></li><li><strong><i>VIVID:</i></strong> bright and eye-catching colors<br></li><li><strong><i>WORLD LADDER:</i></strong> compete with the online leaderboard<br></li><li><strong><i>MUSIC:</i></strong> original soundtrack both funky and soothing<br></li><li><strong><i>ZEN MODE:</i></strong> no obstacles, no score. Pure relax!<br></li><li><strong><i>ATOMIC STUFF:</i></strong> unlock and enable insane post-processing filters</li></ul>",
